1.0.0.name: wordpress/tweaker3
1.0.0.description: A theme specifically built for those who love tweaking their own themes. Open, clean and quick-loading design with a wide sidebar on the right. 'Superfish' drop-down menu built in, caters for all the post formats and also offers user support via a mini forum.
